snippet.title: Darkest Dungeon meets Zombie Apocalypse Day R Survival - The Dead Await
snippet.description:
Free Game Download - store.steampowered.com/app/1682330/The_Dead_Await_Prologue/

Get ready to experience the thrills and chills of The Dead Await: Prologue, a free and fully functional demo! Build your deck and try to survive in this deck-building survival RPG set during a zombie apocalypse. 

▶Patreon Only Gameplay Let's Plays : www.patreon.com/SpicyFalcon
▶Twitter @ Mr Falcon : www.twitter.com/YKYMisterFalcon
